      <p>We accept PhD students through Imperial's Aeronautics doctoral programme. Strong candidates have a background in mechanics, materials, manufacturing, or computational geometry, and ideally hands-on experience with at least one of: 3D printing, FEM, robotics, or fabrication.</p>
