      <p>Funded postdoc positions are advertised here when available. We also welcome applications for fellowships (Marie Skłodowska-Curie, Royal Society, Imperial Schrödinger, etc.) — get in touch early to discuss fit.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="join-card">
      <h2>Undergraduate &amp; MEng</h2>
